'''Suomen Tolkien-seura Kontu ry.''', the '''Finnish Tolkien Society Kontu''' ("Kontu" is the Shire in Finnish) is the Finnish Tolkien society, founded in 1992.

The society publishes ''Hobittilan Sanomat'' ("Hobbiton News") and ''Legolas'' (both with an English summary), which are well recognized [[J.R.R. Tolkien|Tolkien]] publications in Finland.
